<div class="page" id="page-schedule">
  <div class="page-inner" style="max-width:900px;">
    <p class="section-label">The Celebration</p>
    <h2 class="section-title">Schedule of Events</h2>
    <div class="section-divider"></div>
    <p class="schedule-intro">Five days of celebration in the Italian countryside.</p>
    <p class="schedule-note">Palazzo Mannocchi will be ours from August 31st through September 4th, with events taking place September 1st – 3rd and the wedding on September 2nd. We encourage you to make the most of the week and attend everything — but only the wedding day is required.</p>

    <div class="day-block">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-date">Monday, August 31</div>
        <div class="day-label">Arrival</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">4:00 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Check In</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Earliest check-in is 4:00 PM — arrive any time after that. Drop your bags, take a deep breath of Italian air, and settle into Palazzo Mannocchi — your home for the week</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Palazzo Mannocchi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-block">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-date">Tuesday, September 1</div>
        <div class="day-label">Exploration Day</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">12:00 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Exploration Time</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Optional excursions to explore the Marche region — from wine and cheese tastings to e-bike tours. Head to the <a href="#" onclick="showPage('explore');return false;" class="inline-link">Explore page</a> for all the details!</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">4:30 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Chill Poolside Hang</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Grab a drink, find a lounge chair, and soak up the Marche sun — the perfect warm-up for the week ahead</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Palazzo Mannocchi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">7:30 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">&#129346; Welcome Pizza Party</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Our first evening all together — great food, flowing wine, and the excitement of what's to come</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; La Dolce Vita — light colors and breezy vibes</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Three Arches Square</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-block day-block--wedding">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-date">Wednesday, September 2</div>
        <div class="day-label">Wedding Day</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">4:45 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Guests Arrive</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Doors open — please be seated no later than 5:00 PM</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Black Tie Optional</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Panoramic Garden</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">5:15 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">&#128146; Ceremony</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Chang &amp; John say "I do" with a view of the rolling Italian hills</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Black Tie Optional</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Panoramic Garden</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">6:15 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">&#127865; Aperitivo Hour</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Spritzes, cocktails, and antipasti — cheers to the newlyweds!</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Black Tie Optional</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Bell Tower Square</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">7:45 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Dinner &amp; Reception</div>
          <div class="event-desc">A feast under the stars — toasts, tears of joy, and dancing until our feet give out</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Black Tie Optional</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Bell Tower Square</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">11:45 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">&#128378; After Party — Ally's Rave Cave</div>
          <div class="event-desc">The night is young. Descend into the wine cellar for late-night beats and questionable dance moves</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Party vibes — dress to dance</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Palazzo Mannocchi Wine Cellar</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-block">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-date">Thursday, September 3</div>
        <div class="day-label">Recovery &amp; Fun</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">10:30 AM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Post-Wedding Brunch</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Ease into the morning with good food, strong coffee, and even stronger memories from last night</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Palazzo Mannocchi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">3:00 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Beach Day</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Sun, sand, and the Adriatic Sea — the perfect way to recover</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Beach outfit — bring a jacket in case it gets cold</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Porto San Giorgio</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">7:00 PM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Farewell Seafood Dinner</div>
          <div class="event-desc">One last magical evening — fresh catch, sunset views, and sandy toes. The best way to say arrivederci</div>
          <div class="event-dress">&#128087; Beach outfit — bring a jacket in case it gets cold</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Porto San Giorgio</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="day-block">
      <div class="day-header">
        <div class="day-date">Friday, September 4</div>
        <div class="day-label">Departure</div>
      </div>
      <div class="event-item">
        <div class="event-time">10:00 AM</div>
        <div>
          <div class="event-name">Check Out</div>
          <div class="event-desc">Arrivederci, Palazzo! Until we meet again… pack your bags (and maybe an extra bottle of wine)</div>
          <div class="event-loc">&#128205; Palazzo Mannocchi</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
